mm/damon/sysfs: fix wrong empty schemes assumption under online tuning in damon_sysfs_set_schemes()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.12 by commit f98d1f2a36ad7ab48fb4cf73ca14e7b19482fd4d, it was introduced in version v5.19 by commit da87878010e59869d4d27b3c01ecc8ec06ff4a20. For more details please see the references link.
